reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Gets the job done!
reviews.reviewText: If you live with a messy housemate, like I do, this type of organizer for your bathroom is essential in keeping their stuff from migrating all over the limited counter space and making everything difficult to find and get to. This is quite a large organizer and I was amazed to see it held just about everything my wife had on her counter. The only downside I would say is the little basket that hangs off one of the sides that holds longer items. This is a nice way to separate out toothpaste and dental implements from the rest of the items you use daily, but the only issue for me is that, for such a large organizer overall, this basket is quite small. I would have liked something with even 25% more space, as that would make things not quite as cramped with the various toothpastes and brushes that my wife has. Other than that small complaint, I think this is a great way of organizing your stuff. Does it look like it's in a 5-star spa? Maybe not, but it looks good enough to me and a thousand times better with everything on it organized vs. randomly all over the counter, so I guess it depends on whether you are buying this for purely aesthetics or as a minimal investment to vastly improve an otherwise very messy countertop
